text: Takashi Uchiyama (born 18 August 1974) is a Japanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saitama Prefecture
